 The horsemen transformed to robot mode. Turned to see that their leader had 
not yet arrived. They pondered why Kit Kat would send so little forces. 
Megatron would not dare to attack now. Unless they where completely insane. 
And their still was the missing death. What happened to him?

Destructor:: It seemed as if Kit Kat would not allow Drill Bit to go. So he 
looked to dark mouse..."Let us be off. The more time we waste here the more 
chances of our destruction grows." He tried not to show it but when Kit kat 
walked off he was very dissapointed in her. She let her emotions cloud her 
judgment. He turned and flew out of the base not looking back. He was hopeful 
that dark mouse would follow with out a problem. If not then she would only 
get in the way anyway.
